{"tid":713984,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(認真討論) 如果自殺唔會影響他人 其實係咪無問題","createTime":"2018-06-23T09:46:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-24T18:32:18.000Z","uid":18606,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"61d071f631105cb741e2b324487fe6aad696bf42","tid":713984,"uid":18606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T09:46:00.000Z","msg":"舉例 有人無親人 無朋友 而且自殺之後唔會造成其他人麻煩（例如唔使幫佢處理屍體）<br />\n咁自殺會唔會俾大家認同<br />\n<br />\n利申 好愛惜生命 想長命百歲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只係好奇選擇幾時死係唔係可以俾大家選擇 作為一個人嘅權利<br />\n<br />\n認真討論 唔係叫人自殺 搵巴打幫手貼撒馬利亞乜乜乜"},{"pid":"9eebc468415fa4593d9a392f241e912d016e3ca3","tid":713984,"uid":18606,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T09:47:37.000Z","msg":"心智未成熟請按上一頁離開"},{"pid":"ce102454e550395394a6d6fdf144350de6c94622","tid":713984,"uid":44454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T09:50:44.000Z","msg":"係，但係現在左膠當道，所以就算一個人生不如死，左膠都要佢地生存落去"},{"pid":"6e1b70ea12a8d0c3eeef3ac4c567f547b87f8016","tid":713984,"uid":74262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T09:51:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"152a9e2a36d183bbe753bc1aba4c57d2cc1eeb54","tid":713984,"uid":110207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T09:52:27.000Z","msg":"無錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68f62464cc83ae5021a97571c74d4d0fc7b897e7","tid":713984,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T09:53:04.000Z","msg":"如果自殺唔影響人，但又係唔係真係有呢個如果？好似有排有人燒炭死，之後個陣子就會有人有樣學樣燒炭死；正如呢排興氦氣自殺咁。<br />\n<br />\n同埋自殺唔影響人有點，反正都自殺，你唔通仲想人死留名，豹死留皮咩，咪由個社會批判囉。"},{"pid":"e5af02af0fb3764b6997d17edc8cb87522d2561c","tid":713984,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T09:53:11.000Z","msg":"係外國咪有得你揀 香港？返工啦望"},{"pid":"353647a5d5986073da4bbc0a32d4c404096c1613","tid":713984,"uid":49918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T09:56:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6dffe343c381fd00bbec3f3441932d67d98ba277","tid":713984,"uid":37005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T09:58:45.000Z","msg":"當然係 <br />\n唔使俾麻煩人即係冇負擔 冇負擔幾時死都得"},{"pid":"67876d9472710b6d995d972eda66016981050ca2","tid":713984,"uid":3912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T10:02:34.000Z","msg":"死咗之後要人頂你更已經係麻煩到人"},{"pid":"759d1562f81834196a2fbb2ce5dd82cbbd730047","tid":713984,"uid":142313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67876d9472710b6d995d972eda66016981050ca2","tid":713984,"uid":3912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T10:02:34.000Z","msg":"死咗之後要人頂你更已經係麻煩到人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T10:05:36.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n但返學應該點計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa4a084ec926c434a76d1287a6cf3874b0df9e94","tid":713984,"uid":99124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67876d9472710b6d995d972eda66016981050ca2","tid":713984,"uid":3912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T10:02:34.000Z","msg":"死咗之後要人頂你更已經係麻煩到人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T10:09:50.000Z","msg":"咁先劈炮，做足一個月通知呢?"},{"pid":"93fb1eafb0796a9c7090a98102d99fb6f56b520a","tid":713984,"uid":3912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"759d1562f81834196a2fbb2ce5dd82cbbd730047","tid":713984,"uid":142313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67876d9472710b6d995d972eda66016981050ca2","tid":713984,"uid":3912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T10:02:34.000Z","msg":"死咗之後要人頂你更已經係麻煩到人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T10:05:36.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n但返學應該點計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T10:38:30.000Z","msg":"本來考尾二，你一死我變考第尾仆街"},{"pid":"9138fdf